data.description: Grandville Schools, Golf View Estates, Come see this beautiful former parade home on a cul-de-sac street that has a private entrance to Kent Trails. Home Boast, 3 Bedroom 2.5 Bath with possible 4th bedroom (egress window in) and full bath (plumbed) in full  basement. Main floor offers a gorgeous hardwood floor, cathedral ceiling in the living room with a 3 sided fireplace, Kitchen with tiled floors, backsplash, large island, which is perfect for entertaining. Newer stainless appliances, Main floor laundry with butler/storage room, half bath and a pantry. Newer paint through out the home. The spacious second floor features a custom book case and reading nook,  a master suite with vaulted ceiling, Walkin shower. Has a Jack and Jill bedrooms, full tiled bathroom.2.5 stall garage, fenced yard
